snippet.title: Ostrofa - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Be prepared to survive in a beautiful, custom-generated, low poly environment, fighting against other players from all over the world.

Written, developed and scored by Normunds Petrovs.

For beta sign-up, music, game info and more, please visit: https://www.ostrofa.com/
Support development on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/normunds

Keep yourself updated by following us:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ostrofagame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ostrofa
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/ostrofa
